dct_description_sm: Cartographic Details: Scale [1:15,000,000]. Imprint derived from the atlas in which the map was issued."Engraved by S. Hall." Numbered XL. Shows boundaries, rivers and settlements. Relief shown by hachures. Greenwich meridian. Dimensions: 37 x 26 centimeters
